CINAVIA!! Why don't more people mention this??  Huge inconvenience.

For Cinavia there's an easy way to solve it -

After the sound gets muted , exit the movie and go to date time settings . 
Then change the time 1 hour up or down 
Go back play the movie 
Exit once again 
And again change the time back to where it was 
And Voila , play the movie .. but it will play for another 20 min 
Repeat the same ..

Amazing upload, man! I found out about this movie while I was digging for a quality action flick and it absolutely blew me away. It's an adrenaline rush from start to finish, and the fight scenes are some of the best I've ever seen. Even the dubbed dialogue is pretty good - not always perfect, but definitely better than a lot of the dubbed foreign movies on the market today.
